    Find your path
  



    At GROUNDFLOOR, we value personal and professional integrity above all else, while celebrating and cultivating individual talent. We do this by by surrounding ourselves with strong individuals who value collaboration. Are you a big thinker and doer with an interest in our audacious mission to take private lending public? Join us. 
  



    Headquarters
  









          Headquartered at Tech Square in the Midtown area of Atlanta,
         GROUNDFLOOR has created new investment opportunities for non-accredited investors and streamlines access to financing for independent builders.  You may not completely know what all of that means, but we promise we're not just tooting our own horn when we say that what we've built is one-of-a-kind.
        

          If you are interested in helping to create something truly innovative, please get in touch. We are always looking for great people.  And we are also very passionate about chocolate.
        

          Please send your resumé to
          careers@groundfloor.us









