Interaction Designer 


Submit Resumé




GROUNDFLOOR is an Atlanta-based fintech startup opening the market for peer-to-peer lending in real estate. We're looking for an accomplished interaction designer to define, shape and evolve a broad variety of multimodal consumer, B-to-B and internal user experiences. The ideal candidate is motivated by the opportunity to build a distinctive brand, product and service that stands apart in a field of many that aim to reformat banking, finance and investing. As a company, we value and select for intellect, strategic thinking, authenticity and integrity.

