Background in painting and/or illustration highly desirable.
3-5 years experience designing desktop, mobile or web applications.
Expert knowledge of user-centered design principles.
Demonstrable mastery of Photoshop, Illustrator, or other design tools.
Ability to do rapid prototyping in HTML5.
Great written and verbal communication skills.
Excellent collaborative skills.
Highly professional, with the ability to deliver solid work on tight schedules.
Expert level knowledge of graphic design tools, such as: Photoshop and Illustrator.

Description:
GROUNDFLOOR is seeking an Interaction Designer with a passion for great design, a superb aesthetic sense, an exceptional eye for detail and a deep appreciation for and ability to create simple solutions to complex problems.  The ideal candidate is a brilliant problem solver, quick study, self starter, and excellent communicator with a passion for great design and the ability to achieve it. The candidate possesses that rare blend of interaction design, visual design, and prototyping skills. From brainstorming through implementation, the Interaction Designer will work with members of the software, marketing and executive teams. He or she must excel at creating designs that are simple, elegant, useful and trustworthy. Must also possess a relentless attention to detail and an uncommon eye for aesthetic taste and quality.  This person will have a direct influence on the future our of platform.
Education:

Education BS or equivalent in media arts or graphic design related field.


