Brian Dally
Co-Founder & CEO
brian@groundfloor.us








Brian is a co-founder and director of GROUNDFLOOR and serves as our CEO. He is responsible for marketing as well as setting long term direction and goals for the company.
Brian's 15 year career building disruptive technology startups spans stints in Silicon Valley, Boston, London and the North Carolina Triangle region. Previously, he led the launch of Republic Wireless to take on the big four cellphone carriers to international acclaim. As a result, millions more Americans can now afford a smartphone.
Brian has a JD from Harvard Law School, an MBA from Harvard Business School, and a BA with Highest Distinction from the University of Virginia.













