Jason Widen
Advisor




Jason advises GROUNDFLOOR on real estate development and investments.
He has an extensive background in real estate, including investment, property development and property management. Jason has also created an award winning wine cafe & gallery, co-founded Leadership exCHANGE, a global student leadership organization, and co-founded the successful entrepreneurial co-working community HQ Raleigh, where he serves as Executive Director and met Brian. Jason graduated from the University of Denver with a BA in Business Administration, Hotel and Restaurant Management.













