John Mangham
Advisor




Known as "The 1031 Guy", John Mangham has been involved in real estate for almost 4 decades.
A trusted advisor to investors and agents, he is a CPA, licensed real estate broker and most importantly, a very active investor. During the economic downturn, John and his partners raised over $40 Million Dollars in equity and debt for a “buy and hold” fund and an active ongoing “flip” business. Collectively they have bought, sold, renovated, built, and brokered over 500 properties since 2009. John is a graduate of Auburn University and a resident in the City of Atlanta.













